HOW2 DEPLOY ON SERVER ATTHOST.PL

1. IF(server.js) 'server.js' name have to be changed to 'app.js'

2. IF(config.port != 3000) PRODUCTION PORT have to be set to 3000 in config.js

3. copy all files from project to webserver catalogue

example:
COPY
from
    WebStormProjects/node-testapi
to
    ftp-server: wec.atthost.pl user:wec password: c...0 folder on the server /websites/testapi

#without DOCS and SQL-CREATE-DB folders

4. RESTART APP FROM UI AT ATTHOST.PL
-goto Aplikacje
-Wylacz
-Wlacz
-in Szczegoly you see where the APP resides



HOW2 prepare ATTHOST.PL

https://atthost.pl/help/jak-uruchomic-aplikacje-w-nodejs/

